## Manual Caching

```php
$cachePath = __DIR__ . '/../storage/cache/routes.php';

if (file_exists($cachePath)) {
    $router->loadFromCache($cachePath);
} else {
    $router->register(UserController::class);
    $router->register(PostController::class);
    $router->saveToCache($cachePath);
}
```

